SwiftSimStreamer

This project contains code derived from serve-sim by Evan Bacon:
https://github.com/EvanBacon/serve-sim

serve-sim is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

This repository has been substantially modified from the original project:
the TypeScript CLI, React browser UI, middleware, WebSocket server, and npm
workspace were removed; the native simulator framebuffer, accessibility, touch,
and keyboard mechanisms were adapted into a SwiftPM-based macOS SwiftUI app.
